Document: PlaceholderMaterial
Path: godot/classes/class_placeholdermaterial.rst
Summary: A placeholder class for materials in Godot Engine.

Inherits: Material < Resource < RefCounted < Object
Placeholder class for a material. This class serves as a base for implementing custom material types but does not provide any functional material properties or rendering capabilities on its own.
